Setting up virtual environment -> https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N5vscPTWKOk&ab_channel=CoreySchafer

To activate the environment in windows use:  Scripts\activate 
To deactivate the virtual environment in windows use: Scripts\deactivate

Follwing error may pop up in windows, to resolve checkout: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4037939/powershell-says-execution-of-scripts-is-disabled-on-this-system

